									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/tawnylara/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tawny-100x100.png" width="100" height="100" alt="Tawny Lara" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/tawnylara/">Tawny Lara</a></h6>
										Tawny Lara is the author of <em>Dry Humping: A Guide to Dating, Relating, and Hooking Up Without the Booze</em>, co-host of the <em>Recovery Rocks</em> podcast, and co-founder of the vinegar-based botanical beverage, (parentheses). Her newsletter, <em>Beyond Liquid Courage</em>, explores life beyond sobriety.																			</div>
